Radiation dosage during flights
-------------------------------
Question to answer:
- How much radiation (how dangerous amount of radiation) dose does someone gets during a given flight?

Data wish list:
- flight coordiantes with altitude data
- amount of ionizing radiation vs altitute
- Sun's activity data
- seasonal and geographical distribution of high atmospheric radiation

Data:
- simple route data (no altitute)
http://openflights.org/data.html
- flight data with altitude (3 usd, behind paywall)
https://www.flightradar24.com/premium/

! Solved problem !
Solution:
http://jag.cami.jccbi.gov/cariprofile.asp


